---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Call for Papers">
  <article class="cfp-content">
    <h1>Call for Papers</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Early Career Economics Seminar Series (ECESS)</p>

    <section class="intro">
      <p>
        In January 2026, we (Heriot-Watt PhD students) will launch a new biweekly seminar series.
        The goal of this series is to create a low-stakes and accessible space for researchers to present their work, network with peers, and reconnect with alumni.
      </p>
      <p>
        We want this to be a space where you can test ideas and get in a first run-through in public as well as encouraging more socialising. To this end we are imposing two policies:
      </p>
      <ul class="policies">
        <li><strong>Clarifications Only:</strong> We will only permit interruptions to clear up details, otherwise allowing space for presenters to tell their story before discussion.</li>
        <li><strong>Social Focus:</strong> An aim for Monday afternoons, with the specific intention of heading to Geordies for a drink and a chat immediately afterwards.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="target-audience">
      <h2>Who Should Apply?</h2>
      <p>We specifically encourage applications from:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Current PhD students (at any stage)</li>
        <li>Recent alumni and Industry Post-PhDs</li>
        <li>Early Career Researchers</li>
        <li>Visiting peers from other universities</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="formats">
      <h2>Formats</h2>
      <div class="format-grid">
        <div class="format-card">
          <h3>1. Short Form</h3>
          <p><strong>Time:</strong> 15–20 minutes (+ discussion)</p>
          <p><strong>Purpose:</strong> Early-stage ideas, research proposals, or getting feedback on a specific puzzle you are trying to solve.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="format-card">
          <h3>2. Long Form</h3>
          <p><strong>Time:</strong> 45–60 minutes (+ 15 mins Q&A)</p>
          <p><strong>Purpose:</strong> Ideal for polishing a completed paper, practicing a job talk, or presenting a full chapter.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="apply">
      <h2>How to Apply</h2>
      <div class="apply-box">
        <p>We are currently filling slots for the coming second semester (starting Jan 5th).</p>
        <p>If you are interested in presenting, please reply to <a href="mailto:gjm2004@hw.ac.uk">gjm2004@hw.ac.uk</a> with:</p>
        <ul class="checklist">
          <li>Your preferred format (Short or Long)</li>
          <li>A rough title or topic (abstract even better)</li>
          <li>Your preferred dates in January/February/March</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="sign-off">
          Best regards,<br>
          Heriot-Watt ECESS Organisers
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  .cfp-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .subtitle {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: #666;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .intro {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .policies {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--accent-color);
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
  }

  .policies li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .format-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
  }

  .format-card {
    background: #fff;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border: 1px solid #ccc;
    box-shadow: 2px 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    transform: rotate(-1deg);
  }

  .format-card:nth-child(2) {
    transform: rotate(1deg);
  }

  .format-card h3 {
    color: var(--accent-color);
    border-bottom: 1px dashed #ccc;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .apply-box {
    background: #f9f9f9;
    padding: 2rem;
    border: 2px dashed var(--text-color);
    position: relative;
  }

  .apply-box::before {
    content: '✉️';
    position: absolute;
    top: -15px;
    left: 20px;
    font-size: 2rem;
    background: var(--paper-color);
    padding: 0 0.5rem;
  }

  .checklist {
    list-style-type: none;
    padding-left: 0;
  }

  .checklist li::before {
    content: '✓ ';
    color: green;
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .sign-off {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .format-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
